  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 413254fdefae1ac48b7ebe7d580a5ed9, type: 3}
  m_Name: Dialogue_Nere
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  lines:
  - Hey, I heard Carlos already told you what happened with the chests!
  - "But I think I\u2019ve figured out the cause\u2014or at least I think so. At
    the end of the meadow, some kind of dungeon appeared."
  - "And I believe that\u2019s probably the reason! Maybe if you defeat the boss
    in that dungeon, everything will go back to normal\u2026 or not\u2026 I\u2019m
    not sure."
  - "But I\u2019d kill it anyway, because that definitely wasn\u2019t there before."
  voiceClip: {fileID: 8300000, guid: 7412283917459194dbb1598d7b1c1ec5, type: 3}
